sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Server as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant AuthMW as AuthenticationMiddleware
    participant QuotaMW as QuotaMiddleware
    participant OAuth as OAuth2/JWKS Endpoint<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KVStore as SQLite KV Store<br/>(local file)
    participant Router as Inference Router<br/>(Provider Plugin)
    participant vLLM as vLLM Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant VectorDB as PostgreSQL + pgvector<br/>5432/TCP
    participant Tools as Tool Runtime<br/>(Tavily/Brave/MCP)

    Note over Client,Tools: Flow 1: Chat Completion Request

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/inference/chat-completion<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (JWT)
    Server->>AuthMW: Validate token
    AuthMW->>OAuth: GET /.well-known/jwks.json<br/>TLS 1.2+ (public keys)
    OAuth-->>AuthMW: JWKS response
    AuthMW-->>Server: User attributes extracted

    Server->>QuotaMW: Check rate limit
    QuotaMW->>KVStore: Query quota (SQLite)
    KVStore-->>QuotaMW: Quota OK (1000 req/day auth)
    QuotaMW-->>Server: Request allowed

    Server->>Router: Route to inference provider
    Router->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Optional TLS, Bearer Token
    vLLM-->>Router: SSE stream: data chunks
    Router-->>Server: Stream response
    Server-->>Client: SSE stream: text/event-stream<br/>Header: x-trace-id

    Note over Client,Tools: Flow 2: RAG Query (Vector IO + Inference)

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/tool-runtime/rag-tool/query<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Server->>AuthMW: Validate token
    AuthMW-->>Server: Authorized

    Server->>Router: Generate embedding
    Router->>vLLM: POST /v1/embeddings<br/>Optional TLS
    vLLM-->>Router: Embedding vector

    Router->>VectorDB: SELECT with vector similarity<br/>pgvector cosine distance<br/>Optional TLS, Password auth
    VectorDB-->>Router: Matching chunks (top-k)

    Router->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Context: retrieved chunks
    vLLM-->>Router: Generated response
    Router-->>Server: RAG result
    Server-->>Client: JSON response

    Note over Client,Tools: Flow 3: Agent Turn with Tool Execution

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/agents/{id}/session/{sid}/turn<br/>Auth: Bearer Token, SSE
    Server->>AuthMW: Validate token
    AuthMW-->>Server: Authorized

    Server->>Router: Agent runtime: create turn
    Router->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(determine tool calls)
    vLLM-->>Router: Tool call decision<br/>(e.g., web_search)

    Router->>Tools: POST search API<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>API key auth
    Tools-->>Router: Search results

    Router->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(generate final response with tool results)
    vLLM-->>Router: Final response stream

    Router-->>Server: SSE agent turn events
    Server-->>Client: SSE stream: agent steps + response
